  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial will test the efficacy and safety of oral colchicine in prevention of
      proliferative vitreoretinopathy (PVR) in cases of rhegmatogenous retinal detachment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
